lead_paragraph: With a huge dollop of understatement and a wry smile, rank outsider Marcus Willis described the day he faced the greatest player of all time on Wimbledon's Centre Court as "not my standard Wednesday".

headline.print_headline: Not My Usual Wednesday, Says Unlikely Lad Willis
headline.main: Not My Usual Wednesday, Says Unlikely Lad Willis
